## Coordination matrix (Muster)

| Role | DevOps needs | DevOps delivers |
|------|--------------|-----------------|
| **IT-Architect** | ADR: DB host, auth boundary, network | Runbook + compose согласно ADR; новый infra choice → ADR draft |
| **Developer** | `DATABASE_URL`, build args, health route | Working compose, `.env.example` diff, migrate on deploy notes |
| **PM** | Deploy task in queue with AC | `READY` infra tasks → `DONE` with deploy URL / runbook link |
| **QA** | Staging URL, smoke steps | Deploy checklist; fix infra bugs found in smoke |
| **UI/UX** | — | Только если CDN/assets path влияет на static |
| **Growth / CMO** | — | Analytics host — OSS self-host (Plausible/Umami) по ADR Architect |

**Handoff flow (deploy):** Architect ADR (deploy path) → PM task `READY` → **DevOps** (compose, CI, SSL) → Developer (env, health endpoint) → **QA** (smoke) → PM/Human sign-off.

**Parallel agents:** DevOps + Developer на разных task ID ok; DevOps не трогает `IN_PROGRESS` Developer без Human.

